  <H1>After Market Option List - Reports</H1>
  <P>The Reports tab of the After Market Option List shows the Reports available.</p>

	<p>In <b>SCM Reports</b>, a filter is given to filter the business segments and the options with RAS Discontinue Dates
	for the SCM Reports.
	Once the filter is selected, click the <b>View Current SCM Report</b> to see what the current SCM Report would look like if it
	was published. To publish the current SCM Report, click the <b>Publish SCM Report</b> button.
	The SCM Report will include the Completed options.
	</p>

	<p>The <b>Published After Market Option SCM Reports</b> table is filtered depending on the business segment filter.
	To view a particular SCM Report, click the link for the date and time it was published.</p>

	<p>If you want to compare the contents of two previously published SCM Reports, select the two reports in the
	table and click the <b>Compare Published</b> button.</p>

	<p>If you want to compare the contents of a previously published SCM Report and the current live data, select the
	report in the	table and click the <b>Compare with Current</b> button.</p>


